'''Christine Magnuson''' (born [[October 17]] [[1985]] in [[Tinley Park]], [[Illinois]]) is an [[United States of America|American]] [[Swimming (sport)|swimmer]].

==Biography==
Magnuson went to high school at Victor J. Andrew High School in Tinley Park, IL and competed in college for the [[University of Tennessee]].

==2008 Summer Olympics==
